OL,3,CTwo burglars jailed after using dating
OL,4,Capp Grindr to trick victims
OL,6,FTwo burglars have been jailed after
OL,7,Fusing the dating app Grindr to deceive
OL,8,Fvictims into allowing them into their
OL,9,Fhomes, before stealing mobile phones
OL,10,Fand money.
OL,12,FRahmat Khan Mohammadi, 23, and
OL,13,FMohammed Bilal Hotak, 27, arranged to
OL,14,Fmeet their targets at their London
OL,15,Fproperites, Isleworth Crown Court
OL,16,Fheard on Monday.
