OL,6,FThe men would then persuade their
OL,7,Funsuspecting dates to provide them
OL,8,Fwith their phone passwords under the
OL,9,Fguise of wanting to play music on
OL,10,Ftheir device.
OL,12,FThe Afghan refugees then quickly
OL,13,Fexited the properties, taking the
OL,14,Funlocked devices with them which
OL,15,Fallowed them to make online or
OL,16,Fcontactless payments. In some
OL,17,Finstances, they transferred funds
OL,18,Fdirectly to themselves.
