OL,6,FSentencing both men, Judge Adenike
OL,7,FBalogun said: "I have taken note of
OL,8,Fthe psychological trauma as well as
OL,9,Fthe inconvenience caused to the
OL,10,Fvictims, and the distress that all of
OL,11,Fthem have expressed at allowing you
OL,12,Finto their homes ` into their private
OL,13,Fspace ` only to be violated."
OL,15,FProsecutor David Patience had alleged
OL,16,Fthat the men were targeted because of
OL,17,Ftheir sexuality and the offences could
OL,18,Fin effect been seen as hate crimes.
