OL,6,FThe judge said: "I've considered that
OL,7,Fmatter very carefully and it seems to
OL,8,Fme that the presumed sexual
OL,9,Forientation of the victims presented
OL,10,Fan opportunity for you to commit the
OL,11,Fcrime, and in that respect I do find
OL,12,Fthat the victims... were targeted
OL,13,Fbecause of their perceived
OL,14,Fvulnerability."
OL,16,FHowever, she said they were not picked
OL,17,Fbecause the two men held "hostility"
OL,18,Ftowards the victims' sexuality.
