OL,3,CTwo burglars jailed after using dating
OL,4,Capp Grindr to trick victims
OL,6,FTo facilitate the burglary and fraud,
OL,7,Fa Grindr profile was set up that
OL,8,Fnearly always had no photograph. When
OL,9,Fthe victims asked to see an image they
OL,10,Fwould send one of somebody else.
OL,12,FA meet-up would be arranged and, on
OL,13,Fseveral occasions, Mohammadi would ask
OL,14,Fto bring a friend which would be Hotak.
OL,16,FOnce inside they would ask the victim
OL,17,Fto turn on music, usually on YouTube
OL,18,Fbecause the phone could not be locked
OL,19,Fwhile a video was playing.
