OL,6,FA distraction tactic was deployed
OL,7,Fwhere they would request the man
OL,8,Fleaves the room while their phone kept
OL,9,Fplaying the video.
OL,11,FTheir excuses included taking a shower
OL,12,Fbefore sex, making a drink and showing
OL,13,Fone of the perpetrators the toilet.
OL,15,F"In all the cases, when the victim
OL,16,Freturned to the main room you had
OL,17,Fleft, or one or the other of you had
OL,18,Fleft, and the victim found the mobile
OL,19,Fphone was missing," the judge said.
